{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/inilah-para-pemenang-lomba-komik-polisi-millennial-road-safety-festival/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Inilah Para Pemenang Lomba Komik Polisi Millennial Road Safety Festival","content":"\n<p>Pada tanggal 15 Januari hingga 15 Maret lalu, Kepolisian Republik Indonesia bersama dengan grup Author Indonesia dan CIAYO Comics mengadakan <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Lomba Komik Polisi Millennial Road Safety Festival (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://festivalkreatif.com/lomba-komik-polisi/\" target=\"_blank\">Lomba Komik Polisi Millennial Road Safety Festival</a>. Lomba ini diadakan untuk menyambut <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"acara bertajuk sama (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://metro.tempo.co/read/1166787/polda-metro-jaya-gelar-millennial-road-safety-festival-apa-itu\" target=\"_blank\">acara bertajuk sama</a> yang diadakan serentak di seluruh provinsi Indonesia.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53448\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/inilah-para-pemenang-lomba-komik-polisi-millennial-road-safety-festival/attachment/01-lomba-komik-mrsf/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-lomba-komik-mrsf\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" alt=\"Lomba Komik Polisi Millennial Road Safety Festival. Sumber: Festival Kreatif\" class=\"wp-image-53448\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Lomba Komik Polisi Millennial Road Safety Festival. Sumber: Festival Kreatif</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Selama lomba komik ini berlangsung, tercatat lebih dari 100 peserta mengirimkan karya mereka melalui Instagram. Dari seluruh peserta, terpilih 25 besar, kemudian tersisihkan lagi menjadi 10 besar hingga terpilih satu pemenang utama. Tema yang diusung adalah “mewujudkan milenial cinta lalu lintas menuju Indonesia Gemilang.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nah, gimana para peserta meramu tema tersebut ke dalam\nsebuah komik strip yang kekinian namun tetap memiliki pesan bermakna? Biar\nmakin jelas, yuk kita intip karya-karya para pemenang Lomba Komik Polisi\nMillennial Road Safety Festival berikut ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Para Pemenang Lomba Komik Polisi Millennial Road Safety Festival</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Likes Terbanyak: Okky Andrian Lola – Cinta Lalu Lintas Demi Keselamatan Bersama</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53449\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/inilah-para-pemenang-lomba-komik-polisi-millennial-road-safety-festival/attachment/02-lomba-komik-mrsf/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-lomba-komik-mrsf\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Okky Andrian Lola\" class=\"wp-image-53449\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Komik Polisi / Okky Andrian Lola </figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Komik ini menceritakan sepasang kekasih yang berboncengan\nmotor tengah ditegur oleh seorang polwan cantik. Saat sang polwan bertanya\napakah si cowok sudah tidak sayang lagi dengan pacarnya, dia malah berbalik\nmenggoda sang polwan sehingga pacarnya marah. Padahal maksud polwan itu adalah\nkarena pacar si cowok tidak dipakaikan helm.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Juara 4: Septia Indah Rosiana – Cukup, Oma!</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53450\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/inilah-para-pemenang-lomba-komik-polisi-millennial-road-safety-festival/attachment/03-lomba-komik-mrsf/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-lomba-komik-mrsf\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Septia Indah Rosiana\" class=\"wp-image-53450\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Komik Polisi / Septia Indah Rosiana</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagi penyuka film Indonesia tentu sangat mengenal karakter\nRhoma Irama dan kekasihnya Ani. Dalam komik ini, keduanya kembali bersitegang.\nRhoma kecewa karena Ani “meninggalkannya” di tengah jalan. Ternyata keduanya\nmemang benar-benar berhenti di tengah jalan. Mereka pun ditilang polisi karena\nmengganggu lalu lintas serta tidak mengenakan helm. Juara 4 mendapatkan hadiah\nuang tunai 500 juta Rupiah.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Juara 3: Juni Kurniyanto – Milenial Keren</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53451\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/inilah-para-pemenang-lomba-komik-polisi-millennial-road-safety-festival/attachment/04-lomba-komik-mrsf/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-lomba-komik-mrsf\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Juni Kurniyanto\" class=\"wp-image-53451\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Komik Polisi / Juni Kurniyanto</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Komik ini menceritakan tentang dua teman yang tengah\nmenikmati makan siang. Saat satu dari mereka membayangkan betapa kerennya\npengendara motor gede di luar, temannya memberi tahukan hal-hal yang membuat\nseorang pengendara motor terlihat lebih keren. Kuncinya adalah dengan membawa\nkelengkapan saat berkendara serta mematuhi peraturan lalu lintas. Juara 3 mendapatkan\nhadiah uang tunai 1.5 juta Rupiah.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Juni Kurniyanto yang dikenal sebagai Elkurnia ini salah satu author <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komik-dilan-1990-ciayo-comics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"komik Dilan 1990 (opens in a new tab)\">komik Dilan 1990</a> loh! Jangan lupa cek karyanya di CIAYO Comics!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Juara 2: Achmad Arsad – Cinta Lalu Lintas Sejak Dini</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53452\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/inilah-para-pemenang-lomba-komik-polisi-millennial-road-safety-festival/attachment/05-lomba-komik-mrsf/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-lomba-komik-mrsf\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Achmad Arsad\" class=\"wp-image-53452\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Komik Polisi / Achmad Arsad</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Komik ini merupakan salah satu episode dari serial komik\nNaila Syala Lala. Dalam komik ini, Naila diantar oleh ayahnya ke TK, dimana di\nsana ia belajar tentang pentingnya menaati peraturan lalu lintas. Saat dijemput\nayahnya, Naila menceritakan pengalamannya belajar bersama pak polisi.\nMasalahnya, ayah Naila datang dengan motor tapi tidak pakai helm, sehingga\ndipelototi pak polisi yang mengajari Naila barusan. Juara 2 mendapatkan hadiah\nuang tunai 3 juta rupiah.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Juara 1: Bikindong Creative – Ketika Ayah Mengantar Ke Sekolah</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53453\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/inilah-para-pemenang-lomba-komik-polisi-millennial-road-safety-festival/attachment/06-lomba-komik-mrsf/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-lomba-komik-mrsf\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Bikindong Creative\" class=\"wp-image-53453\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/06-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Komik Polisi / Bikindong Creative</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Juara 1 dari Lomba Komik Polisi Millennial Road Safety\nFestival jatuh kepada Bikindong Creative yang membuat komik tentang seorang\nayah yang mengajari anaknya tentang berbagai adab berlalu lintas. Komik yang\nminim unsur komedi ini benar-benar menekankan pentingnya membiasakan diri untuk\npatuh dan taat pada peraturan, karena nanti akan menjadi sebuah kebiasaan yang\ndijalankan dari dalam hati. Juara 1 mendapatkan hadiah uang tunai 5 juta\nrupiah!</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Pemenang 10 besar juga akan mendapatkan piagam dan merchandise resmi dari CIAYO Comics, Kepolisian RI, dan Indo Tactical Gear. Penasaran dengan komik-komik 10 besar lainnya? Nantikan di artikel selanjutnya, dan baca langsung komik-komiknya <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"di CIAYO Comics (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/komik-polisi\" target=\"_blank\">di CIAYO Comics</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53474\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/inilah-para-pemenang-lomba-komik-polisi-millennial-road-safety-festival/attachment/07-lomba-komik-mrsf/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/07-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-lomba-komik-mrsf\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/07-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/07-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/07-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53474\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/07-lomba-komik-mrsf.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/07-lomba-komik-mrsf-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"2a49325c-5f48-5041-839a-3a7fc9abb8ef"}}}